    "diffSummary": "Pre-credential hardening. Set a restrictive Content-Security-Policy on the Tauri webview in src-tauri/tauri.conf.json (was csp:null): script-src 'self', style-src 'self' 'unsafe-inline' (Svelte/Tailwind inline styles), img-src self+asset protocol, connect-src 'self' ipc: http://ipc.localhost so Tauri IPC keeps working. Fixed the placeholder window/document title in src/app.html to 'Zalo Desktop'. Added @types/node to package.json devDependencies and removed the now-stale @ts-expect-error in vite.config.js, making svelte-check report 0 errors / 0 warnings. No credential, login, or storage code introduced.",
